leTestJava was executed due to earlier changes, it should detect updates in the classpath and proceed accordingly.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Understanding Gradle classpath**\\n\\nThe SourceSets output directory includes generated classes separately, which is interesting. Even with a stale build in `build/classes`, the classpath could be ordered differently. For example, `testClasses` might include the generated directory. However, if Gradle's test classpath looks at `build/classes/java/test` before the generated directory, it could lead to issues with stale classes shadowing newer ones. I need to ensure that stale files are overwritten, so compileTestJava is likely to execute, which should help resolve the issue.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Fixed the `ClassFormatError: Truncated class file`.\n\nRoot cause: the generated replacement bytecode for:\n\n`io/restassured/internal/RequestSpecificationImpl$_removeUnnamedPathParamByValue_closure4.class`\n\ncontained the static initializer bytes, but its class-file `methods_count` was still `5` instead of `6`. The JVM therefore interpreted the `<clinit>` method bytes as malformed class attributes, producing the truncated class-file error.\n\nChanges made in:\n\n`tests/src/io.rest-assured/rest-assured/5.5.0/build.gradle`\n\n- Corrected the generated class bytecode so the method count includes `<clinit>`.\n- Bumped:\n\n```groovy\ninputs.property(\"directAccessClassesVersion\", \"remove-unnamed-path-param-by-value-closure4-v3\")\n```\n\nso `generateDirectAccessClass` is forced to regenerate the class on the next Gradle run.\n\nI verified the embedded class with `javap`; it now disassembles correctly and includes:\n\n```text\nstatic java.lang.Class class$(java.lang.String);\n  Code:\n     0: aload_0\n     1: invokestatic java/lang/Class.forName\n     4: areturn\n     ...\n```\n\nand:\n\n```text\nstatic {};\n  Code:\n     0: ldc \"java.lang.Object\"\n     2: invokestatic class$\n     5: pop\n     6: return\n```\n\nI did not run the Gradle tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_072c8cfa52234539016a0124da484881978dcd469ae98fd0ac\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1423, "output": 1054, "cacheRead": 83968, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 86445, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778459850013, "responseId": "resp_072c8cfa52234539016a0124cb39f08197b30704f7617474eb"}, "toolResults": []}
